title: 15 Minute Beginner Workout: Treadmill Virtual Scenery (Slow Jog/Fast Walk)
description:
15 Minutes of Virtual Scenery for your Treadmill. The pace is a slow jog or fast walk. Good for beginners:)

The setting is a beautiful bridge over water.

Check out my other walking videos here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLs2S4w7G9RePBYggRtkcnhRtfMDYobqFZ
channelDescription:
Hello fellow adventurers! Here you will find walking, nature, and other adventure videos.
Need inspiration to get fit and reach your life goals? Join me in virtual walking and running on scenic trails. Meditate with me and learn how to overcome your fears that may be holding you back from reaching your life dreams.
